{"tid":847152,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"轉完台 手機收唔到任何認證sms","createTime":"2018-10-04T03:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T23:01:45.000Z","uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6223df1552dcfc1c6cb7a95b74995b783a315290","tid":847152,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的 9月份我就由csl轉去smartone (number冇轉)<br />\n轉完之後我電話就收唔到任何驗證用既sms eg 網上信用卡 銀行login之類<br />\n我打過去銀行佢地話睇到有record有sms比我<br />\n我都打去smartone又話我network冇問題<br />\n但最撚奇怪我淨係收到smartone既sms<br />\n連朋友send比我都收唔到<br />\n利伸： 我用緊iphone 6s <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打有冇試過呢個情況<br />\n收唔到sms上網買唔到野好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2de963e3e152ff93eee988ea051afe6a5d15d7f","tid":847152,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"你有冇試過第二部電話收sms<br />\n我都係csl轉smt,但無任何問題"},{"pid":"bca8694589dd1d9b71c0475736167c61961fb44b","tid":847152,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2de963e3e152ff93eee988ea051afe6a5d15d7f","tid":847152,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"你有冇試過第二部電話收sms<br />\n我都係csl轉smt,但無任何問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"今晚返去試下 <br />\n但如果真係收到 <br />\n即係部電話出現問題？<br />\n我冇裝咩block sms既野<br />\nsetting又冇搞過佢"},{"pid":"59eeff4836459ae8814e995568db9b3e8fca686b","tid":847152,"uid":10068,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"Check下信息中心號碼係咪+85290100000<br />\n<br />\n打*#5005*7672# 可以check到<br />\n如果check咗唔啱就打以下code去改<br />\n**5005*7672*SMSCNUMBER# 更改訊息中心(國際格式)<br />\n都係唔得就用下面個code, delete 咗設定再auto update 網絡商設定<br />\n##5005*7672# 刪除訊息中心設定"},{"pid":"ac31a1f6f7f9a53ce6424f2fca4db5b263ad0bc8","tid":847152,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p